Package com.intellij.openapi.editor.markup

Class TextAttributesEffectsBuilder

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.intellij.openapi.editor.markup.TextAttributesEffectsBuilder

  • public class TextAttributesEffectsBuilder
extends java.lang.Object
    Allows to build effects for the TextAttributes. Allows to cover effects on the current state and slip effects under it.

      • coverWith

        public final TextAttributesEffectsBuilder coverWith(TextAttributes attributes)
        Applies effects from attributes above current state of the merger. Effects may override mutually exclusive ones. E.g If current state has underline and we applying attributes with wave underline, underline effect will be removed.

      • slipUnder

        public final TextAttributesEffectsBuilder slipUnder(TextAttributes attributes)
        Applies effects from attributes if effect slots are not used.

      • coverWith

        public TextAttributesEffectsBuilder coverWith(EffectType effectType,

        Applies effect with effectType and effectColor to the current state. Effects may override mutually exclusive ones. E.g If current state has underline and we applying attributes with wave underline, underline effect will be removed.
